EvacSim.jme3tools.navmesh

Class NavMesh

  • java.lang.Object
    • EvacSim.jme3tools.navmesh.NavMesh
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.jme3.export.Savable, java.io.Serializable

    public class NavMesh
extends java.lang.Object
implements com.jme3.export.Savable, java.io.Serializable
    A NavigationMesh is a collection of NavigationCells used to control object movement while also providing path finding line-of-sight testing. It serves as a parent to all the Actor objects which exist upon it. Portions Copyright (C) Greg Snook, 2000
